    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1h0004-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_010-25a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-09-08T06:49:20.757+09:00">Il ne se repaissait ni de riz blanc</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_010-25a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-09-08T07:11:08.616+09:00">ni de viande finement tranchée. 119 [cf. Anne Cheng p. 76: il n'y a pas lieu d'éviter tranches fines ou mets délicats.(!)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:19:40.554+09:00">je ne veux pas non plus l'imposer aux autres.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:19:13.391+09:00">Ce que je ne veux pas que les autres m'imposent,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:19:49.659+09:00">Le Maître dit:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:20:34.673+09:00">"Si [Zigong],</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-15a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:20:39.091+09:00">tu ne peux y atteindre."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_020-13a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2024-10-09T00:00:18.202+09:00">******If by dint of wishing for perfect morality one achieves perfect morality, 　【cf ch. 2:仁遠乎？ 我欲人斯仁至矣。】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_020-13a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2024-10-09T00:02:35.695+09:00">then who else is there left who will be indignant (for being passed over)?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-25a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-04-05T18:30:45.161+09:00">Le Maître dit,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-25a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-04-05T18:31:24.177+09:00">La vie de l'homme consiste dans la droiture; </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-26a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-04-05T18:32:35.949+09:00">s'il la perd il doit à la chance d'avoir la vie sauve.</seg>
                </p>
